# Claude Compatibility Guide

This repository is Claude-first.

This file exists as a compatibility entrypoint for AGENTS-based tools.

Read these files first and in this order before exploring the wider repository:
1. `CLAUDE.md`
2. `.claude/manifest.md`
3. `.claude/config/runtime.yaml`
4. `README.md`
5. `.claude/config/project-surfaces.yaml`
6. `.claude/config/quality-gates.yaml`
7. `.claude/config/review-scope.yaml`
8. `.claude/config/trigger-derivation.yaml`
9. `.claude/config/finding-contract.yaml`
10. `.claude/config/workflow.yaml`
11. `.claude/config/reviewers.yaml`
12. `.claude/policies/quality.md`
13. `.claude/policies/review-scope.md`
14. `.claude/policies/finding-quality.md`
15. `.claude/policies/release-readiness.md`

Default behavior:
- Treat `CLAUDE.md` and `.claude/` as canonical for this project.
- Treat `AGENTS.md` and `.codex/manifest.md` as compatibility shims.
- Do not recursively consume the entire repository unless the task requires working on specific project files.
- Follow the Claude-first read order verbatim so runtime defaults and mandatory policies stay authoritative.
- If `.claude/config/lightning.yaml` is enabled or the task is about optimization, then read `.claude/policies/lightning-boundaries.md`, `.claude/config/lightning.yaml`, and `.claude/config/telemetry.yaml` before proceeding.
